                                <head>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                                </head>
                                <p>No record of the substance of this meeting has been found. The
                                    information given here as to the meeting and the participants is
                                    taken from the Log, <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, p. 554, which
                                    states that the discussions continued after lunch until 3 p.
                                    m.</p>
